info.title: Contact
info.description:
Use contacts to represent the relationship between contacts and accounts. 

This API allows you access to all central information for a contact such as contact name and assignment of the contact to the main account including the business address details of that relationship. Disclaimer: The list of entity type collections displayed under API References is not complete. To view the comprehensive list, see the service metadata.
